    <item>
      <title>阿曼国家能源公司排除增持 OQ Chemicals 的股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/oman-s-state-energy-firm-rules-out-equity-boost-for-oq-chemicals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿曼国家能源公司已排除对其子公司 OQ Chemicals 进行股权注入的可能性，这将危及其今年到期的近 10 亿美元贷款的再融资计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/oman-s-state-energy-firm-rules-out-equity-boost-for-oq-chemicals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 14:44:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国2月份职位空缺增加，工厂订单反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-02/us-job-openings-rise-in-february-factory-orders-rebound-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国 2 月份职位空缺数在上月下调至 874.8 万个后有所增加，而工厂订单继 1 月份下降后增长 1.4%。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台上详细分析了这些数字。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-02/us-job-openings-rise-in-february-factory-orders-rebound-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 14:23:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
